hadiths[145]{hadithnumber,text}:
1556,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee aur unke baad Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko khalifa banaya gaya aur qabaayel arab mein se jinhon ne kufr ikhtiyar karna tha, unhoney kufr ikhtiyar kar liya , to Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap logon se kis bina par qitaal ( jang ( karengey? halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma gaey hain : ''mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke logon se qitaal karun yahan tak ke wo (لا إله إلا الله) kahen . to jisney (لا إله إلا الله) kaha, usney mujh se apna maal aur apni jaan ko mehfooz kar liya , siwaey iske ke Islam ka koi haq ho, aur unka hisab Allah ke zimmey hai.'' us par Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : qasam Allah ki ! main her us shakhs se laaziman jang karunga jo Namaz aur Zakat mein farq kerega kyonkey Zakat maal ka (sharaee) haq hai. qasam Allah ki ! agar un logon ne mujh se wo rassi bhi rok li jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ada kiya kartey they to main uskey rok leney par bhi un se jang karunga. to Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : qasam Allah ki ! maine dekha ke Allah taala ne us jang ke liye Abu-Bakar ka seena khol diya hai aur bil-aakhir meri samajh mein bhi ye baat aa gaee ke yehi baat haq hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye hadees Ribah bin Zaid aur Abdur-Razzaaq ne Maamer sey, unhoney Zohri se usi ki sanad se riwayat ki hai. baaz ne ( uqaala ( '' rassi '' ka lafz bayan kiya hai, jabkey ibne-Wahab ne Yunus se ( عناقا ( '' bakri ka bachcha '' riwayat kiya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Shuaib bin Abi Hamza , Maamer aur Zubaidi ne bhi Zohri se is hadees mein isi tarah kaha hai (ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ( (لو منعوني عناقا) ''agar un logon ne mujh se bakri ka eik bachcha bhi rok liya to . ... '' aisey hi Anbasaa ne Yunus sey, unhoney Zohri se lafz : ( عناقا ( ''bakri ka bachcha'' riwayat kiya hai."
1557,Yunus ne Zohri se ye hadees riwayat kartey huey kaha ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maal ka haq hai ke Zakat ada ki jaey. aur is riwayat mein lafz : (uqaala) ''rassi'' bayan kiya.
1558,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''paanch oonton se kam mein Zakat nahin. aur paanch auqiya (chaandi) se kam mein Zakat nahin. aur paanch wasq se kam ( ghalley ( mein Zakat nahin.''
1559,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf nisbat kartey huey bayan kartey hain : ''paanch wasq se kam ( ghalley ( mein Zakat nahin.'' aur eik ''wasq'' saath (60) maiyaari ''saa'' ka hota hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke Abul-Bakhtari ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se barahe-rast nahin suna.
1560,Janab Ibrahim Nakhai (Rahimahullah) ka bayan hai ke eik wasq saath mohar lagey huey hajjaaji saa ka hota hai.
1561,Habib Maaliki ka bayan hai ke eik shakhs ne (sahibe Rasool) Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aey Abu-Najeed ! aap log hamein kuch aisi ahadis bayan kartey hain jin ki asal hamein Quran mein nahin milti . is par Hazrat imran (Raziallahu anhu) ghussey mein aagey aur us se kaha : kya tumhen Quran mein ye milta hai ke har chaalis dirham main eik dirham ( Zakat ( hai? aur har itni itni tadaad bakriyon main eik bakri hai? aur itney itney oonton mein ye kuchh (Zakat) hai? kya tum logon ko ye sab Quran mein milta hai? usney kaha : nahin. Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : to tum ne ye (masayel aur ehkam) kis se liye hain? bila-shuba tum ye ham ( Sahaba ( hi se letey ho aur ham ne unhen Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se liya hai. (Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ne) is tarah ki aur bhi kaee chizen zikr kin.
1562,Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ''أمابعد ! bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein hukm diya kartey they ke jo maal ham tijarat ke liye tayyar keren us se sadqa ( Zakat ( diya keren .''
1563,Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo ( Shuaib ( apney dada ( Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain ke eik khatoon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaeen . unke sath unki baiti bhi thi aur baiti ke haath mein soney ke do motey motey kangan they. aapney us khatoon se puchha : ''kya tum uski Zakat deti ho?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''kya tumhen ye baat achhi lagti hai ke qiyamat ke roz Allah tumhen unke badley aag ke do kangan pahnaaey?'' chunanche us aurat ne unko utaara aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney dal diya aur kehney lagi : ye Allah aur uskey Rasool ke liye hain.
1564,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main soney ke haar pehna karti thi. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya ye khazana hain? aapney farmaya : ''jo Zakat ki miqdaar ko pahunch jaey aur uski Zakat ada kar di jaey to wo khazanz nahin hai.''
1565,"Abdullah bin Shaddad bin Haad kehtey hain ke ham ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan gaey to unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laye . aapney dekha ke merey haathon mein chaandi ki) moti moti ( angoothiyaan hain to aapney puchha : '' Aaisha ! ye kya hai?'' maine arz kiya : maine unhen aap ki khatir zeenat ke liye pehna hai aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney puchha : ''kya tum inki Zakat deti ho ?'' maine kaha : nahin, ya usi tarah ki koi baat ki . aapney farmaya : ''tujhey jahannam mein ley janey ke liye yehi kafi hai.''"
1566,Sufiyan ne umr bin Ya'laa se riwayat ki aur anguthi wali hadees ki manind zikr kiya. ... . Sufiyan se puchha gaya ke uski Zakat kaisey dey? (yani anguthi waghera ki) to unhoney farmaya : doosrey zewrat ke sath mila ley (aur nisaab ke mutabiq Zakat dey.)
1567,"Hammad bayan kartey hain ke maine ye tehreer Janab Samama bin Abdullah bin Anas se hasil ki hai. wo kehtey they ke isey Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye likha tha jabkey unko sadqe ke liye tahseeldaar bana ke bheja tha aur is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mohar thi. ... is mein tehreer tha : ye fariza Zakat ki tafsil hai jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musalmanon par farz kiya tha, jis ka Allah ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya tha. so jis bhi musalman se iskey mutabiq mutalba kiya jaey, wo ada karey aur jis se uskey alawa mazeed manga jaey to wo na dey . pachchis (25) se kam oonton mein) Zakat bakriyon ki soorat mein hai.). har paanch oonton par eik bakri hai. jab pachchis (25) ho jaeyn to un main eik binte-makhaz (eik baras ki mada oontni) hai, paintis(35) tak . agar un mein koi eik baras ki) binte-makhaz) na ho to do baras ka nar oont dey ( jisey ibne-laboon kehtey hain). aur jab chhattees ()36 ho jaeyn to un mein do saal ki mada oontni ( binte-laboon) hai, paintaalees (45) tak . aur jab chhiyaalees (46) ho jaeyn to un mein hiqqa hai) teen saal ki mada oontni ( jo jufti ke laaiq ho, saath (60) tak . jab iksath (61) ho jaeyn to un mein jaz'aa (chaar saal ki mada oontni ( hai, pachhattar (75) tak . aur jab 76 ho jaeyn to un mein do adad binte-labun (do-do baras ki mada oontniyaan ( hain, nawwey (90) tak . aur jab ikkyanwe (91) ho jaeyn to un mein do adad hiqqa ( teen teen saal ki mada oontniyaan ( hain, jo jufti ke laaiq hun, eik so bees tak. aur jab eik so bees se badh jaeyn to her chaalis mein binte-laboon (do saal ki mada oontni) aur her pachas mein hiqqa (teen saal ki mada oontni) hai. agar Zakat mein wajib honey waley janweron ki umaron mein farq ho, to jis par jaz'aa lazim ho ( chaar saal ki mada ( magar uskey paas jaz'aa na ho balke (is se kam umr ( hiqqa ( teen saal ki oontni (ho to us se hiqa ley li jaey aur wo uskey sath do bakriyan mila dey agar muyassar hon ya bees dirham (chaandi ke). aur jis par Zakat mein hiqqa ( teen saal ki) wajib hui ho, magar uskey paas hiqqa na ho balke jaz'aa (chaar saal ki) ho to us se jaz'aa ley li jaey aur tahseeldaar usko bees dirham dedey ya do bakriyan. aur jis par hiqa ( teen saal ki oontni ( wajib hui ho magar mojud na ho balke binte-laboon (do saal ki mada) ho to us se binte-laboon ley li jaey. ... . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : hadees ke is hissey ke baad mujhey apney shaikh Musa bin Ismael se kama hiqa zabt nahin hai. ... aur sahibe maal uskey sath do bakriyan dey agar muyassar hon, ya bees dirham . aur jis par Zakat mein binte-laboon (do saal ki mada) lazim aai ho magar uskey paas hiqqa (yani teen saal ki mada) ho to us se wo hiqqa ley li jaey. ...  Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : us hissey ke baad mujhey khoob zabt (control) hai. ... aur tahseeldaar usey bees dirham dey dey ya do bakriyan . aur jis par binte laboon ( do saala mada ( laagoo hui ho magar uskey paas eik saala ( binte-makhaz) ho to us se wohi qubul kar li jaey aur sath do bakriyan li jaeyn ya bees dirham . aur jis par binte-makhaz (eik saala mada) lazim aai ho magar uskey paas do saala nar ( ibne-laboon) maujud ho to us se wohi ley liya jaey magar uskey sath kuch ( wapis ( nahin hoga. aur jis shakhs ke paas sirf chaar oont hon to us par koi Zakat wajib nahin hai siwaey iske ke unka Malik chahey . aur charney wali bakriyon ki Zakat ( ki tafsil ( ye hai ke chaalis se lekar eik sau bees tak main eik bakri hai. agar us se badh jaeyn to do bakriyan hain do sau tak . do sau se ziyada mein teen bakriyan hain, teen sau tak . agar bakriyan teen sau se badh jaeyn to har har sau main eik eik bakri hai. Zakat mein koi boodhi ya aeb daar bakri na li jaey aur na bakra ( jufti wala nar ( hi liya jaey siwaey iske ke tahseeldaar Zakat ki khahish ho. aur Zakat ke khauf se do alehda rewadon ko jama na kiya jaey aur na ikhattey maal ko alehda alehda kiya jaey. aur jin do mushtarak malikon ka maal ikhatta ho aur Zakat ikhatti hi li gaee ho to wo aapas mein barabar barabar len-den kar len. agar kisi ki jangal mein charney wali bakriyan chaalis ki ginti ko na pahunchti hon to un mein koi Zakat nahin siwaey iske ke unka Malik chahey . chaandi mein chaliswan hissey hai. agar maal sirf eik sau nawwey dirham ho to us mein koi Zakat nahin siwaey iske ke uska Malik chahey."
1568,"Saalim apney walid ( Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se naqal kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zakat ki tafsil likhi thi magar usey apney aamilon ki taraf bhejney na paey they ke aap ki wafaat ho gaee jabke aapney usko apni talwaar ke sath ( niyaam mein) rakha hua tha. chunanche Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us par amal kiya yahan tak ke unki wafaat ho gaee , phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne amal kiya yahan tak ke unki wafaat ho gaee . is mein ye tehreer tha : ''paanch oonton main eik bakri , das mein do bakriyan , pandarah mein teen bakriyan aur bees mein chaar bakriyan hain. pachchis oonton main eik saala mada oontni ( binte-makhaaz ( hai, paintis tak . agar eik bhi badh jaey to us mein binte-laboon ( do saala oontni ( hai, paintaalees tak . agar eik bhi badh jaey to un mein hiqqa ( teen saala oontni ( hai, saath tak . agar eik bhi badh jaey to un mein jaz'aa hai) chaar saala oontni ( pachhattar tak . agar eik bhi badh jaey to un mein do binte-laboon ( do do saal ki oontniyaan ( hain, nawwey tak . agar eik bhi badh jaey to un mein do hiqqa ( teen teen saal ki mada ( hain, eik sau bees tak . agar oont is se ziyada hon to har pachas main eik hiqqa ( teen saal ki mada (aur har chaalis main eik binte-laboon ( do saala ( hai, aur bakriyon mein har chaalis main eik bakri hai, eik sau bees tak . agar eik bhi badh jaey to do bakriyan hain do sau tak . agar do sau se eik bhi ziyada ho jaey to us mein teen bakriyan hain teen sau tak . agar bakriyan is se ziyada hon to har sau main eik bakri hai. aur sau se kam mein kuch nahin yahan tak ke sau puri ho jaeyn . ikhattey janweron ko Zakat ke andeshey se alehda alehda na kiya jaey aur alehda alehda ko jama na kiya jaey. aur jinkey janwer ikhattey hon wo dono aapas mein barabar barabar len den kar len . aur Zakat mein koi boodha ya aeb wala janwer na liya jaey. Imam Zohri kehtey hain ke jab Zakat wasul kerney wala aaye to bakriyon ko teen hisson mein baant liya jaey yani halkey , umda aur darmiyaney darjey mein aur tahseeldaar Zakat darmiyaney darjay se ley . Imam Zohri ne gaayon ka zikr nahin kiya."
1569,Sufiyan bin Husain ne apni (mazkura baala (sanad se aur usi ke ham-maani bayan kiya. ... aur kaha : ''agar binte-makhaaz ( eik saala oontni ( na ho to ibne-laboon ( do saala nar ( pesh kar dey.'' aur Zohri ka kalam zikr nahin kiya.
1570,"Janab ibne-Shahab ne kaha : ye naqal hai us tehreer ki jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sadqa (Zakat) ke baarey mein likhi thi aur ye aale-Umar bin Khattab ke paas mehfooz thi. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : isey mujhey Salim bin Abdullah bin umr ne padhwaya aur maine isko usi tarah yaad kar liya aur yehi wo tehreer hai jisey Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ne Abdullah bin Abdullah bin umr aur Salim bin Abdullah bin umr se naqal karwaya tha. ... aur hadees bayan ki . kaha : ''jab ( oonton ki tadaad ( eik sau ikkis (121) ho jaey to un mein teen binte-laboon ( do do saala mada ( hain, eik sau untees tak . jab eik sau tees ho jaeyn to un mein do binte-laboon (do do saala mada (aur eik hiqqa ( teen saala mada ( hogi , eik sau untaalees tak . aur jab eik so chaalis ho jaeyn to un mein do hiqqa ( teen teen saala mada (aur eik binte-laboon ( do saala mada ( hogi eik sau oodanchas (149) tak . jab eik sau pachas ho jaeyn to un mein teen adad hiqa hongi ( teen teen saala mada ( eik sau unsath tak . jab eik sau saath (160)  ho jaeyn to un mein chaar adad binte-laboon hongi eik sau unhattar tak . jab eik sau sattar ho jaeyn to un mein teen adad binte-laboon aur eik hiqqa hogi eik sau unasi (179) tak . jab eik sau assi ho jaeyn to us mein do adad hiqqa aur do adad binte-laboon hongi , eik sau nawaasi tak . jab eik so nawwey ho jaeyn to un mein teen adad hiqqa aur eik binte-laboon hongi, eik sau ninnanwey tak . aur jab do sau ho jaeyn to un mein chaar adad hiqqa ya paanch adad binte-laboon hongi , jis umr ka janwer bhi ho, ley liya jaey. aur charney wali bakriyon mein . ''hadees Sufiyan ibne Husain ki manind zikr kiya. is mein hai : ''sadqey mein koi boodhi ya aeb daar bakri na li jaey aur na nar bakra , siwaey iske ke tahseeldaar Zakat chahey.''"
1571,"Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ka farman hai : mutafarriq maal ko jama ya ikhattey maal ko juda juda na kiya jaey. wo yun ke maslan her shakhs ki chaalis chaalis bakriyan hon jab tahseeldaar Zakat lene aaye to wo apney maal ko ikhatta karkey dikhayen , taake us main eik bakri hi aaye. aur ikhattey maal ko juda juda na kiya jaey. yani do khaleet ( shareek ( hon aur her eik ki eik sau eik (101) bakri ho (majmua do so do) to us mein teen bakriyan Zakat hai magar tahseeldaar Zakat ki aamad par ye apney apney maal ko juda juda kar lein to her eik par sirf eik eik bakri aaeygi. (is tarah eik bakri bacha lein.) uski maine yehi tafsil suni hai."
1572,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, ( raawi hadees ( Zuhair kehtey hain ke merey khayal mein unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya, aapney farmaya : ''chaaliswan hissey ada karo, her chaalis dirham mein se eik dirham. aur jab tak do sau dirham purey na ho jaeyn , tum par kuch lazim nahin. jab do sau dirham ho jaeyn to un mein paanch dirham (Zakat) hai. aur jo is se ziyada ho wo usi hisab se hai (is ka chaaliswan hissey Zakat di jaey.) aur bakriyon mein har chaalis main eik bakri hai. ye agar untaalees hon to tum par un mein kuch nahin.'' aur unki tafsil usi tarah bayan ki jaisey ke Zohri ki riwayat mein bayan ho chuki hai. aur gaayon bailon ki Zakat mein farmaya : ''har tees janweron main eik saala bachda hai aur her chaalis mein do saala . aur aisey janwer jin se kaam liya jata hai un par koi Zakat nahin. aur oonton ki Zakat '' . ... sabiqa hadees Zohri ki manind bayan ki . kaha : ''pachchis oonton mein paanch bakriyan hain. agar eik bhi badh jaey to un main eik binte-makhaz ( eik saala mada ( hai. agar binte-makhaz na ho to ibne-labun muzakkir ( do saala oont ( , paintees tak .''  agar eik bhi badh jaey to un main eik binte-labun hai) do saala mada ( paintaalees tak . jab eik bhi badh jaey to un main eik hiqqa hai) teen saala mada ( jo jufti ke qabil ho, saath (60) tak . phir hadees Zohri ki manind bayan kiya. aur kaha : ''agar eik bhi badh jaey yani ikkyanwe ho jaeyn to un mein do hiqqey hain jo ke juftii ke qabil hon. eik sau bees tak. jab oonton ki tadaad is se ziyada ho jaey to har pachas main eik hiqqa  (teen saala mada) hai. Zakat ke khauf se ikhattey janweron ko juda juda na kiya jaey aur na alehda alehda ko jama kiya jaey. aur Zakat mein koi boodha ya aeb daar ya nar ( jufti wala ( janwer na liya jaey, siwaey iske ke tahseeldaar chahey (nar ley sakta hai). aur zarai ajnaas mein jo zameenein darya ya barish se sairab hoti hon un mein daswaan hissa hai aur jo dol (rahat, tube wail waghaira) se sairab hoti hon un mein beeswaan hissey hai.'' Aasim aur Haris ki riwayat mein hai : '' Zakat har saal hai.'' Zuhair ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unhoney kaha : ''(har saal) eik baar hai.'' Aasim ki riwayat mein hai : ''agar oonton mein binte-makhaz ( eik saala mada (ya ibne-labun ( do saala nar ( na ho to das dirham ya do bakriyan dey.''"
1573,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain. . . . . . iska kuchh ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey wohi hai jo ooper mazkur hua . ... kaha : ''jab tumharey paas do sau dirham hon aur un par eik saal guzar jaey to un par paanch dirham ( Zakat ( hai. aur soney mein tum par kuch nahin yahan tak ke tumharey paas bees Dinar hon, isliye jab tumharey paas bees Dinar hon aur un par eik saal guzar jaey to un par aadha Dinar ( Zakat ( hai aur jo ziyada ho to wo isi hisab se hoga .'' (Abu-Is'haaq ne ( kaha : mujhey nahin maloom ke ''isi hisab sey, , wali baat Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne khud kahi hai ya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki janib se.'' aur kisi maal par Zakat nahin yahan tak ke us par saal guzar jaey.'' (raawi hadees) Jarir ka bayan hai ke ibne-Wahab hadees mein ye izafa kartey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''kisi maal par Zakat nahin yahan tak ke us par saal guzar jaey.''"
1574,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine (tum sey) ghodey aur ghulam ki Zakat maaf kar di hai. so tum chaandi ki Zakat lao , her chaalis dirham main eik dirham aur eik sau nawwey dirham mein koi Zakat nahin. jab do sau ho jaeyn to un mein paanch dirham hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is hadees ko Aamash ne Abu-Is'haq se riwayat kiya hai jaisey ke Abu-Awaana ne kaha hai, isi ke sath Sheban Abu-Muaawia aur Ibrahim bin Tahmaan ne Abu-Is'haq sey, unhoney Haris sey, unhoney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se isi ke jaise riwayat kiya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Abdullah bin Muhammad Nufaili ki hadees (sabiqa : 1572) Shoba aur Sufiyan waghaira ne Abu-Is'haq sey, unhoney Aasim sey, unhoney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai magar marfoo nahin kaha hai balke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf kiya hai."
1575,"Behaz bin Hakeem apney walid sey, wo unke dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her chaalis oonton mein jo ke jangal mein chartey hon, eik binte-labun ( do saala mada ( hai aur unhen unke hisab se juda juda na kiya jaey. jo shakhs ajr aur sawab ki niyat se dega . ... . ibne-al-Ula ne ( مؤتجرا بها (ke alfaz kahe . ... . to iskey liye uska ajr aur sawab hai aur jo ( Zakat ko) rokey ga to ham us se wasul karengey aur aadha maal ( mazeed bhi) ye hamarey Shan wale Rab ke waajibaat mein se eik wajib hai, is mein aale-Muhammad ka koi hissey nahin hai.''"
1576,Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab unko Yaman ki taraf bheja to farmaya tha : ''gaayon mein har tees main eik saala bachda ya bachhiya lena aur har chaalis mein se do saala. aur har (ghair Muslim) baligh se eik Dinar ya uskey barabar muaafiri kapda jo ke Yamen mein hota hai.''
1577,Janab Masruq ne Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ke misl bayan kiya.
1578,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko Yaman ki taraf bheja , aur usi ke jaisi zikr ki. is riwayat mein ye zikr nahin hai ke ''ye kapdey hain jo Yaman mein hotey hain.'' aur na lafz (محتلما) hi zikr kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is riwayat ko Jarir , Yaala , Maamer , Shoba Abu-Awaana aur Yahya bin Saeed ne Aamash sey, unhoney Abu-Waeil sey, unhoney Masruq se ( mursal ( naqal kiya hai, jabkey Yaala aur Maamer ne Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ke misl ( muttasil ( bayan kiya."
1579,"Suwaid bin Ghafala bayan kartey hain ke main ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aamil ke sath ( chala , ya kaha ke mujhey us shakhs ne bayan kiya jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aamil ke sath raha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehad ( tehreer ( mein ye tha : ''Zakat mein koi doodh wala janwer (bakri waghaira) ya doodh peeta bachcha na lena , juda juda janweron ko jama na karna aur na ikhattey ( rehney , charney walon ( ko juda juda karna.'' aur aap Alehissalam ka tahseeldaar Zakat unke paaniyon ( chashmon , kunon ya taalaabon ( par pahunchta tha, jab bakriyan pani peeney ke liye aati thin , to wo ( malikon sey) kehta tha : apney maalon ki Zakat pesh karo . raawi ne bayan kiya : chunanche eik shakhs ne ( كوماء ( oontni ka qasad kiya. raawi kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Abu-Saaleh ! ( كوماء (ka kya maani hai? kaha : badey kohan wali . to aamil ne leney se inkar kar diya (kyonkey wo bahut umda thi ( maal waley ne kaha : main pasand karta hun ke aap meri behtareen oontni wasul keren magar usney leney se inkar kar diya. to wo dusri pakad laya jo us se zara kam darjey ki thi. to usney wo bhi leney se inkar kar diya. chunanche wo eik aur ley aaya jo us se bhi kam darjay ki thi to usney wo ley li aur kehney laga : main ye ley to raha hun magar andesha hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujh par khafa hongey. aap mujhey kahengey ke tum us aadmi ki behtareen oontni ley aaye ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hasheem ne Hilal bin Khabbab se usi ki manind riwayat kiya magar lafz (la yufarriqu) istimal kiya."
1580,Suwaid bin Ghafala (Rahimahullah) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka tahseeldaar Zakat hamarey yahan aaya . maine uska haath pakad liya aur uskey wasiqey mein padha : '' Zakat ke khauf se juda-juda rehney waley janweron ko jama na kiya jaey aur na ikhattey maal ko alehda alehda kiya jaey.'' is riwayat mein) Raze-labn ( '' yani doodh waley janwer ya doodh peetey bachchon.'' ka zikr nahin hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke (لا تجمع) ''tum jama na karo.'' aur (لا تجمع) '' jama na kiye jaeyn .'' ka eik hi hukm hai.
1581,"Muslim bin Shoba bayan kartey hain ke Janab Naafe bin Alqama ne merey walid ko unki apni qaum ka sarbarah , nigraan kaar aur muntazim bana diya aur hukm diya ke in se Zakat bhi wasul karen. chunanche merey walid ne mujhey (Muslim ko) eik jamaat ke paas bheja , main eik badey buzurg ke paas pahuncha unka naam Siar ( bin-Wesam ( tha. maine arz kiya : merey walid ne mujhey bheja hai ke aap se Zakat ley aaun . unhoney kaha : aey bhatijey ! tum kis qism ka maal letey ho? maine kaha : ham chun kar thanon ko dekh kar umda bakriyan letey hain. wo kehney lagey : bhatijey ! main tumhen eik hadees bayan karta hun. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein un wadiyon mein se eik wadi main apni bakriyon ke sath tha ke merey paas do aadmi aaye jo eik oont par Sawar they. unhoney mujh se kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se aap ke paas aaye hain taake aap apni bakriyon ki Zakat dey den . maine puchha : mujh par un mein se kya wajib hai? unhoney kaha : eik bakri . to maine eik bakri ka qasad kiya jo main janta tha ke wo doodh aur charbi se bhari hui thi. main usey unki taraf nikal ley aaya . to wo kehney lagey : ye to hamila hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamila janwer leney se mana farmaya hai. maine kaha : aap log kis tarah ki qubul karengey ? wo kehney lagey : eik saal ki bheed ya bakri , jo doosrey saal mein ja lagi ho ya do saal ki jo teesrey saal mein shuru ho. ab main eik bheed ley aaya jo moti tazi thi aur hamila na hui thi. . . . . .) mohtaat ( wo bakri jo hamila to na hui ho magar us umr ko pahunch chuki ho. . . . . . wo mein unke liye nikal laya to unhoney kaha : ye hamein dey do , to unhoney usko apney sath oont par rakh liya aur chal diye. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : Abu-Aasim ne Zakariya se riwayat kartey huey raawi ka naam Muslim bin Shoba kaha hai, jaisey ke rooh ne bayan kiya hai."
1582,"Zakariya bin Is-haq ne apni sanad se ye hadees bayan ki aur raawi ka naam Muslim bin Shoba zikr kiya (na ke Muslim bin ثفنہ ). is mein zikr kiya : (Shaafe) wo hoti hai jiskey pet mein bachcha ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : maine hims mein aale Amr bin Haris Himsi ke yahan Abdullah bin Salim ki kitab mein padha , jisey unhoney zubaidi se riwayat kiya tha, kaha : (Abdulla bin Muawiya al Ghaziree) jo Ghazira Qais se hain, kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney teen kaam kiye usney emaan ka zaiqa chakh liya . jisney eik Allah ki ibadat ki aur iqrar kiya ke Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin. aur khushi khushi her saal apney maal ki Zakat di , koi boodha , khaarish zada , bimar ya raddi qism ka janwer na diya balke mutwassit maal se diya. bila-shuba Allah taala ne tum se umda maal ka mutalba nahin kiya hai aur na tumhen bura maal deney ka hukm diya hai.''"
1583,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh ko sadqey ka aamil bana kar bheja , main eik aadmi ke paas pahuncha , jab usney merey samney apna maal jama kar diya to maine us par sirf eik binte-makhaz ( eik saala oontni ( hi wajib pai . maine us se kaha : eik binte-makhaz dey do , tumhari yehi Zakat hai. usney kaha : ye doodh wali hai, na sawari ke qabil ! uski bajaey ye eik jawan aur moti tazi oontni hai usey ley jao . maine us se kaha : jis ka mujhey hukm nahin hai main wo kyonkar ley sakta hun, aur Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tum se qarib hi hain agar chaho to unki khidmat mein chaley jao aur jo kuchh mujhey dey rahey ho unhen ja kar pesh kar do agar aap qubul kar lein to mujhey bhi qubul hai agar wo na-manzur keren to main bhi qubul nahin karta : kehney laga : main yehi karta hun, chunanche wo merey sath chal pada . aur wo oontni bhi sath ley gaya jo wo mujhey dey raha tha yahan tak ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunch gaey . usney aap se kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! aap ka numaainda merey maal ki Zakat leney ke liye merey yahan pahuncha hai aur qasam Allah ki ! is se pehley na tu Allah ke Rasool merey maal mein tashrif laye hain aur na unka koi numaainda hi . so maine uskey liye apna maal jama kya to usney bataya ke merey maal mein sirf eik binte-makhaz wajib hai, aur is umr ka janwer na doodh deta hai aur na sawari ke qabil hota hai. so maine usey eik shandaar jawan oontni pesh ki ke usey qubul kar ley magar usney inkar kar diya, aur wo ye rahi ! aey Allah ke Rasool ! main usey aap ki khidmat mein ley aaya hun to aap qubul farma lijiye , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''tujh par wohi farz hai lekin agar to khushi se neki karna chahey to iska Allah taala tujhey ajr aur sawab ata kerega aur ham tujh se ye qubul kar letey hain.'' usney kaha : aur wo ye rahi aey Allah ke Rasool ! main isey ley aaya hun to aap isey qubul farma lijiye , chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey wasul kar leney ka hukm diya aur uskey maal mein barkat ki dua farmaee."
1584,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman bheja aur farmaya : ''tum eik aisi qaum ke paas ja rahey ho jo ehle-kitab hain, unhen shahadat toheed ( La-ilaah-illallah ( ki aur is ( shahadat ( ki ke main Allah ka Rasool hun, dawat dena . agar wo tumhari ye baat tasleem kar lein , to unhen batana ke Allah ne un par her din raat mein paanch namaazen farz ki hain. agar wo ye bhi maan len to unhen batana ke Allah ne un par unke maalon mein sadqa ( Zakat ( farz ki hai, jo unke maldaron se lekar unke faqiron mein baanti jaeygi . agar wo ye baat maan len to unke umda maalon se perhez karna aur mazloom ki bad dua se bachna , bila-shuba mazloom ki bad-dua aur Allah ke darmiyan koi parda nahin hota.''"
1585,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Zakat wasul kerney mein ziyadti kerney wala, isi tarah hai jaisey ke Zakat na deney wala.''"
1586,"Hazrat Bashir ibne-al-Khasasiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, ibne Ubaid apni riwayat mein kehtey hain ke unka naam pehley Bashir na tha balke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye naam rakha tha. wo bayan kartey hain ke ham ne kaha : Ummaal (governors) ( ehle ( sadqa ham par ziyadti kartey hain, to kya jis qadr wo ziyadti keren ham apna maal chupa liya keren? aapney farmaya : ''nahin.''"
1587,Ayub ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya. albatta unhoney kaha ke ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Zakat wasul kerney waley karindey ziyadti kartey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : isey Abdur-Razzaaq ne Maamer se marfoo riwayat kiya hai.
1588,"Abdur-Rehman bin Jabir bin Ateek apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' an-qareeb tumharey paas kuchh naa-pasandida log aaeyngey . jab wo tumharey paas ayen to unhen khush aamadeed kehna aur unke aur jo wo lena chahen , unke darmiyan aadey na aana . agar unhoney adl aur insaf kiya to uska unhen ajr milega aur agar zulm kiya to uska wabal uthaeyn gey. tum unhen razi rakhna , bila-shuba tumhari Zakat ki takmil unko razi rakhney mein hai aur unhen chahiye ke tumharey liye duaaey khair karen. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Abul-Ghasn se murad Sabit bin Qais bin Ghasn hai."
1589,Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas kuchh dehati log aaye aur unhoney kaha : baaz ummaal (governors) hamarey paas aatey hain aur ham par zulm kartey hain. aapney farmaya : ''apney sadqa wasul kerney walon ko razi rakho.'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! chahey (chaahen) wo ham par zulm keren? aapney farmaya : ''apney Zakat wasul kerney walon ko razi rakho.'' Usman (bin Abi Sheba) ne izafa kiya : ''agar-che tum par ziyadti ki jaey. Abu-Kaamil ne apni hadees mein bayan kiya. Jarir ne kaha : ye farman nabwi sun leney ke baad se aamil hamesha mujh se razi hi gaya hai.
1590,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke merey walid un logon mein se they jinhon-ne (Baiate- Rizwaan ke mauqe par) darkht ke nichey baiat ki thi , aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan jab bhi koi qaum apni Zakat lekar aati thi to aap unhen yun dua detey they : (اللهم صَلِّ عَلَى آلِ فلان) ''aey Allah ! aale-fulan par apni rehmat nazil farma (aur inhen barkat dey . aey Allah ! aale Abi Aufi par apni rehmat nazil farma (aur inhen barkat dey).''"
1591,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada ( Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' na (جلب) hai aur na (جنب) aur unke maalon ki Zakat unke gharon hi par wasul ki jaey.''"
1592,"Muhammad bin Is-haq (Rahimahullah) ne (لا جلبَ wla جنبَ) ki tauzeeh mein bayan kiya : ''chopayon ki Zakat unke apney deron par wasul ki jaey, (جلب ye hai ke) unhen tahseeldaar Zakat (aamil) ke paas khinch kar na laya jaey aur (جنب) is fareezey mein ye hai ke janweron waley unhen door na ley jaeyn. (ibn Is-haq ne kaha) aamil ko munasib nahin ke wo Zakat walon ke maqamat se bahut door ja baithey aur janweron ko uski taraf laya jaey balke Zakat unki apni jagah par li jaey.''"
1593,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah ki raah main eik ghoda diya, phir dekha ke usey bechaa ja raha hai to unhoney usey kharida lena chaha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is baarey mein puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey mat kharido aur apna sadqa mat wapis lo.''"
1594,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghodey aur ghulam mein Zakat nahin, albatta ghulam ki taraf se sadqa fitr diya jaey.''"
1595,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman par uskey ghulam aur ghodey mein Zakat nahin.''"
1596,"Janab Salim bin Abdullah apney walid se naqal kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo khetiyan barish se sairab hoti hon ya daryaon aur chashmon se ya zameen ki tari se to un mein daswaan hissey hai. aur jo oontniyon se ( rahat ke zariey sey) sairab ki jati hon ya jin ki aap-paashi ki jati ho to un mein beeswaan hissey hai.''"
1597,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo zameen daryaon se sairab hoti ho ya chashmon se to un mein daswaan hissey hai. aur jin ko oontniyon se ( rahat ke zariey sey) sairab kiya jata ho to un mein beeswaan hissey hai.''
1598,Janab Wakee ne bayan kiya ke (البعل الكبوس) se murad wo kheti hai jo barish se sairab hoti ho. ibne Aswad kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Adam ne kaha ke maine Abu-Ayaas Asadi se (ba'al) ke mutalliq wazahat poochhi to kaha : jo kheti barish se sairab hoti ho. Nazar bin Shumeil ne kaha : (ba'al) se murad barish ka pani hai.
1599,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko Yaman ki taraf ( aamil bana kar) bheja to un se farmaya : ''ghalley se ghalla , bakriyon se bakri , oonton se oont aur gaayon se gaey wasul karna . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke maine Misr main eik kakdi ko naapaa to usey tera baalisht lambi paya. isi tarah eik oont par eik turanj (naarangi) ladi dekhi ke do tukdey karkey barabar barabar rakhi gaee thi."
1600,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada ( Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain ke bani Muta'aan ka eik aadmi Hilal , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein apney shehad ka ushr (zakat) lekar aaya aur aap se darkhast ki ke ''(سلبة)'' wadi uskey naam kar di jaey, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wo uskey naam kar di. jab Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa baney to Hazrat Sufiyan bin Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) ne likhit taur par Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se uskey baarey mein puchha : to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne likha : agar ye apney shehad ka wohi ushr (zakat) deta rahey jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko diya karta tha, to wadi (سلبة) usi ke naam rehney do. warna ye shehad ki makkhiyaan hain jo chahey (unka shehad) khaye."
1601,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se bayan kartey hain ke shaaba , bano Faham ke talluq-daar they (shaaba chhoti biradari ka naam hai aur Faham badey qabiley ka ( aur saabiqa bayan ki hadees ke jaisi bayan ki . (Mughira ke walid Abdur-Rehman bin Haris ne) kaha : shehad ki her das mushkon mein se eik mushk di jaey. aur (Umar bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke aamil) Sufiyan bin Abdullah Saqafi ne zikr kiya. aur kaha ke unke naam do waadiyaan likh di gaee thin (jabkey Amr bin Haris ne eik wadi ka zikr kiya hai) Abdur-Rehman ne mazeed kaha : chunanche wo log wohi kuch ada kartey rahey jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko diya kartey they aur ye waadiyaan unhi ke naam rahin."
1602,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke qabeela Faham ka eik giroh . ... uskey baad hadees Mughira ki manind bayan ki, kaha : das mushkon mein se eik mushk ( detey they (aur dono waadiyaan unhi ke liye makhsus rahin."
1603,"Janab Zohri ne Saeed bin Musaiyab sey, unhoney Hazrat Itaab bin Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya : ''angooron ke kachchey phal ka andaza lagaya jaey jaisey ke khajuron ka lagaya jata hai. aur unki Zakat kishmish ki soorat mein wasul ki jaey, jaisey ke khajuron mein khushk khajoor ki soorat mein li jati hai.''"
1604,Muhammad bin Saleh Tammar ne ibne-Shahab se unki sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Saeed ( ibn Musaiyab ( ne Hazrat Itaab se kuchh nahin suna.
1605,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Masood bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Sehal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) hamari majlis mein aaye aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya tha : ''jab tum darakhton par phalon ka andaza laga lo , to tum unka phal utaar saktey ho aur andaza kiye huey phal se teesra hissey chhod diya karo. agar tum teesra hissey na chhodo , to chotha hissey chhod diya karo. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke andaza kerney wala apney amal ke takhmeene ke baais teesra hissey chhod dey."
1606,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne khaibar ke silsiley mein zikr kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Abdullah bin Rawaahaa (Raziallahu anhu) ko yahudiyon ki taraf bheja kartey they aur wo khajuron ke phalon ka andaza lagaya kartey they jabkey wo khoob tayyar ho jatey , khaney ke qabil honey se pehley pehley ye kaam kiya jata."
1607,"Janab Abu-Umama bin Sehal apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya tha ke) جعرور (aur ( لون الحبيق ( qism ki) raddi ( khajuren sadqey mein qubul ki jaeyn . Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne wazahat ki ke ye Madiney ki khajuron ki do qismon ke naam hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke isko Abul-Waleed ne bhi ba-waasta Sulaiman bin Kasir , Imam Zohri se musnad zikr kiya hai."
1608,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan masjid mein tashrif laye jabke aap ke haathon mein asaa tha aur kisi ne raddi qism ki khushk si khajuron ka eik guchchaa latka diya tha, aapney apni lathi se is guchey mein thokaa diya aur farmaya : ''ye sadqa kerney wala is se umda bhi sadqa kar sakta tha.'' aur farmaya : ''ye shakhs qiyamat ke roz raddi khajuren hi khaye ga.''"
1609,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sadqae-fitr ko farz qarar diya taake rozey ke liye fuzul aur bekar aur behudaa aqwal aur kaamon se pakizgi ho jaey aur miskeenon ko tuaam (khaana) hasil ho. chunanche jisney isey Namaze ( eid ( se pehley pehley ada kar diya to ye aisi Zakat hai jo qubul kar li gaee aur jisney usey Namaz ke baad ada kya to ye aam sadqaat mein se eik sadqa hai.
1610,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein sadqae fitr ke mutalliq hukm farmaya tha ke usey logon ke Namaze eid ki taraf janey se pehley pehley ada kar diya jaey. (Naafe ne) kaha : Hazrat Ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) isey eid se eik do din pehley hi ada kar diya kartey they.
1611,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ramazan mein sadqae fitr farz farmaya , is tarah ke her musalman azad , ghulam , mard aur aurat ki taraf se khajoor ya jau ka eik saa diya jaey."
1612,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sadqae-fitr eik saa muqarrar farmaya. aur mazkura baala riwayat Malik ke ham-maani bayan kiya. aur mazeed kaha : chhotey aur badey ki taraf se diya jaey. aur hukm diya ke usey logon ke Namaz ke liye nikalney se pehley pehley ada kar diya jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke Abdullah Al Umri ne Naafe ki riwayat mein (على كل مسلم) aur Saeed Jamhi ke b-waasta Ubaidullah ki Naafe ki riwayat mein (من المسلمين) ke lafz bayan huey hain. magar mashhoor ye hai ke Ubaidullah ki riwayat mein (من المسلمين) ke lafz nahin hain.
1613,"Hazrat Abdullah ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney sadqae fitr farz farmaya eik saa jau ya khajoor ka jo her chhotey badey , azad aur ghulam par wajib hai. Musa bin Ismael ne ''mard aur aurat'' ke lafz bhi kahe. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is riwayat mein Ayub aur Abdullah Umri bhi Naafe se (ذكر أو أنثى) ''mard aur aurat '' ke alfaz bayan kartey hain."
1614,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein jau , khajoor , baghair chilkey ke jau ya kishmish mein se eik eik saa sadqae fitr ada kiya kartey they. Janab Naafe kehtey hain, Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aaya aur gehun ki kasrat ho gaee to unhoney un ashiya ke eik saa ki bajaey gehun ka aadha saa muqarrar kar diya."
1615,"Janab Naafe ne kaha ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke phir log gehun ka aadha saa deney lagey . unhoney kaha ke Hazrat Abdullah khajoor diya kartey they magar eik saal ehale-Madina ko khajoor ki tangi aa gaee , to unhoney jau diye ."
1616,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham mein mojud they to ham har chhotey badey , azad aur ghulam ki taraf se sadqae fitr mein tuaam (khana), paneer, jau, khajoor ya kishmish ( mein se kisi eik (ka eik saa diya kartey they. aur ham ye usi tarah detey rahey yahan tak ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) hajj ya Umerey ke liye aaye aur member par chadh kar logon ko khutba diya. minjumla aur baaton ke unhoney logon se ye bhi kaha : main samajhta hun ke shaam ke gehun ke do mud ( aadha saa ( khajoor ke eik saa ke barabar hai. chunanche logon ne unki baat ley li . is par Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main to jab tak zinda hun eik saa hi deta rahun ga. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : ye riwayat ibne Aleh aur Abda waghaira ne ba-sand ibne Ishaq, Abdullah bin Abdullah bin Usman bin Hakeem bin Hizam, Ayaaz,  Abi Saeed, se iskey ham-maani riwayat ki hai. aur is main eik aadmi ne ibne Aleh ki riwayat mein (أو صاعا من حنطة) ''ya eik saa gehun ka'' zikr kiya hai, magar ye mehfooz nahin hai."
1617,"Musaddad ba-waasta Ismael ki riwayat mein ''gehun'' ka zikr nahin hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Muawiya bin Hisham ne Sauri se marwi (bayan) is hadees mein Abu-Saeed sey, , gehun ka aadha saa ''zikr kiya hai magar ye Muawiya bin Hisham ka ya un se riwayat kerney walon mein se kisi ka weham hai."
1618,"Janab Ayaaz kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kehtey they ke main to hamesha eik saa hi deta rahunga . ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein khajoor , jau , paneer ya kishmish mein se eik saa hi diya kartey they. ye riwayat Yahya ki hai. Sufiyan ki riwayat mein (صاعا من دقيق) ''eik saa aatey ka'' zikr bhi hai. Haamid ne kaha : Ulamaaye hadees ne is izaafey par inkar kiya to Sufiyan ne usey bayan karna chhod diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye izafa ibne-Uena ka weham hai."
1619,"Janab Abdullah bin Saulab ya Saulab bin Abdullah bin Ubai Suair apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''har do afrad chhotey badey , azad ghulam , mard aur aurat ki taraf se eik saa gehun hai. chunanche jo tum mein se ghani hai tu Allah taala usey paak kar dega aur jo faqeer hai tu Allah taala usey us se ziyada ata farmaeyga jo usney diya.'' Sulaiman ne apni riwayat mein ''ghani aur faqeer'' ka izafa kiya hai. (yun kaha : azad ghulam , mard aurat ''ghani aur faqir'' ki taraf se. ...)"
1620,"Janab Abdullah bin Saulab bin Abi Suair apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutbey ke liye khadey huey to aapney sadqae fitr ka hukm irshad farmaya ke her fard ki taraf se eik saa khajoor ya eik saa jau diya jaey. Ali ki riwayat mein ye izafa hai ke ya do afrad ki taraf se eik saa gehun ka diya jaey. ... . is hissey se baad ki riwayat mein (Ali bin Hasan aur Muhammad bin Yahya Neshaapuri) dono muttafiq hain ke chhotey, badey , azad aur ghulam ki taraf se diya jaey."
1621,ibne-Juraij ka bayan hai ke ibne-Shahab ne (raawi ka naam) ''Abdullah bin Saulba'' hi riwayat kiya hai. aur Ahmed bin Saleh ne isko (العدوی) kaha . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke wo dar-haqeeqat (العذری) hai. (riwayat ye hai ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eidul-fitr se do din pehley logon ko khutba diya. . . . . . . aur) Abdullah bin Yazid makki) Muqri ki (mazkura baala) riwayat ki manind bayan kiya.
1622,"Janab Hasan Basri bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Ramazan ke aakhir mein Basra mein member par khutba diya aur kaha : apney rozon ka sadqa ada karo . to goya logon ko unki baat samajh mein na aai , to unhoney kaha : ehale-Madina mein se yahan kaun hai? utho aur apney bhaiyon ko samjhao, ye nahin jantey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye sadqae farz farmaya hai ke her azad , ghulam , mard , aurat , chhotey aur badey ki taraf se khajoor ya jau se eik saa diya jaey, ya gehun ka aadha saa. ... aur jab Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to unhoney qeematon me kami dekhi , to farmaya : Allah taala ne tum par wusat farmaee hai so agar tum har chiz se eik eik saa hi diya karo) to behtar aur afzal hai ). Humaid bayan kartey hain ke Janab Hasan (Rahimahullah) Ramazan ka sadqa usi shakhs par lazim samajhtey they jisney rozey rakhey hon."
1623,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko sadqaat wasul kerney ke liye bheja to ibne Jameel , Khalid bin Waleed aur Abbas ne Zakat na di to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ibn Jameel, to is baat ka badla leta hai ke wo faqeer tha, tu Allah ne usko ghani kar diya hai. raha Khalid bin Waleed , to tum us par zulm kartey ho. usney to apni zirhen aur deegar saman Shan Wale Allah ki raah mein dey diya hai. aur rahey Abbas , to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chacha hain, unki Zakat mujh par hai balke isi qadr aur bhi.'' phir farmaya : ''kya tujhey maloom nahin ke insan ka chacha uskey baap ke jaisa hota hai.''"
1624,"Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke kya sadqa (Zakat) lazim honey se pehley usey ada kya ja sakta hai? to aapney unhen iski rukhsat di. ( raawi ne ( eik baar yun riwayat kiya : (فأذن له في ذلك) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : is hadees ko Hasheem ne Mansoor bin Azan sey, unhoney Hakam sey, unhoney Hasan bin Muslim sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai. ... . aur Hasheem ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai."
1625,Ibrahim bin Ata ke walid se riwayat hai ke Ziyad ne ya kisi aur Ameer ne Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko sadqaat ( Zakat ( wasul kerney ke liye muqarrar kiya. jab wo wapis aaye to Ameer ne Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : maal kahan hai? unhoney jawab diya : kya aapney mujhey maal (jama kerney) ke liye bheja tha? ham ne Zakat wasul ki jahan se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein liya kartey they aur wahin laga di jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein lagaya kartey they. (ilaqey ke maldaron se lekar wahan ke fuqaraa aur miskinon mein taqseem kar di.)
1626,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs maangey, halanke iskey paas ba-qadr kifaayat mojud ho, to qiyamat ke roz wo aaeyga aur uska chehra zakhmi hoga ya us par kharaashen hongi ya nocha hua hoga. ''kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ghani honey ki kya miqdaar hai? aapney farmaya : ''pachas dirham ya is qeemat ka sona.'' Yahya ne kaha : Abdullah bin Usman ne Sufiyan se kaha : mujhey to aisey yaad hai ke Shoba Hakeem bin Jubair se riwayat nahin karta hai, to Sufiyan ne jawab diya ke hamein ye riwayat Zubeda ne Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid se bayan ki hai."
1627,"Banu Asad ke eik shakhs se marwi (bayan) hai, usney kaha : main aur merey ghar walon ne Baqeea Al Gharqad (maujud qabristaan Madina) ke paas padaaw kiya, to merey ghar walon ne mujh se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jao aur aap se kuch mang lao ke usey ham kha saken, aur phir wo apni zarooriyaat ginwaaey lagey. chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , maine aap ke yahan eik shakhs ko paya jo aap se kuch mang raha tha aur aap farma rahey they : ''main koi aisi chiz nahin paata jo tumhen dun.'' phir wo aadmi pusht pher kar chala gaya aur wo naraz tha aur keh raha tha : qasam meri umr ki ! aap jisey chahtey hain dey detey hain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye isliye mujh par ghussay ho raha hai ke merey paas kuch nahin hai jo main usey dun? tum mein se jab koi sawal karta hai, halanke uskey paas chaalis dirham ya uskey masaawi (barabar) kuchh ho to usney chimat kar) be-ja ( manga hai.'' is Asadi shakhs ne bayan kiya : maine kaha : hamari oontni to eik auqiya se bahut behtar hai. ... . aur eik auqiya chaalis dirham ka hota hai. ... . wo kehta hai : chunanche main lot aaya aur aap se kuch na manga . iskey baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jau aur kishmish aa gaee to aapney us mein se hamein bhi inayat farmaya. ... . ya usi tarah se kaha . ... . yahan tak ke Allah taala ne hamein ghani kar diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Sauri ne aisey hi riwayat kiya hai jaisey ke Malik ne kaha hai."
1628,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs maangey , halanke uskey paas eik auqiya ( chaalis dirham (ke masaawi (barabar) maujud ho to uska sawal ilhaaf  hai.'' (be ja israr hai.) maine kaha : meri yaaqoota oontni eik auqiya se bahut behtar hai. Hisham ki riwayat mein hai : chaalis dirahmon se bahut behtar hai. chunanche main lot aaya aur aap se kuchh na manga . Hisham ki riwayat mein izafa hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik auqiya chaalis dirham ka hota tha."
1629,"Hazrat Sehal ibne Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Uena bin Hisn aur Aqraa bin Haabis (Raziallahu Anhuma) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur aap se sawal kiya. to jo kuch unhoney manga , aapney unhen dey deney ka hukm diya aur Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke unhen iski eik tehreer dey do , to Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne un dono ko , jo unhoney manga , likh diya. chunanche Aqraa ne wo khat liya , apni pagdi mein lapetaa aur chal diya. magar Hazrat Uena wo khat lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aa gaya jahan aap tashrif farma they aur kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! aap ka kya khayal hai ke , saheefa mutalmmis ki tarah main ye khat lekar apni qaum ke paas chala jaun , na maloom is mein kya hai? to Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne iski talmeeh ki wazahat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney pesh ki. (is ki tafsil fawaaid mein darj hai) tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(jo shakhs maangta hai, halanke ba-qadr kifaayat uskey paas mojud ho to wo apney liye aag hi ka izafa karta hai.'' Nufaili ne dusri jagah kaha : ''jahannam ke angaarey ziyada karta hai.'' logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo kya ( miqdaar ( hai jo insan ko kafi hoti hai (aur sawal se ghani bana deti hai?) dusri jagah Nufaili ke alfaz is tarah they. ghinaa (maaldaari) ki wo kya had hai jiskey hotey huey sawal karna layaq nahin? aapney farmaya : ''jiskey paas subah aur shaam ka khana maujud ho'' Nufaili ke alfaz dusri jagah ye they. ''jiskey paas din aur raat ke liye pet bhar khana maujud ho.'' (Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain) Nufaili ne hamein ye riwayat mukhtasar taur par isi tarah bayan ki thi jo zikr ki gaee hai."
1630,Hazrat Ziyad bin Haris Sadaai (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se baiat ki . ... . aur lambi hadees bayan ki . ... aur kaha : phir eik shakhs aap ki khidmat mein aaya aur kehney laga ke mujhey sadqe mein se kuchh dijiye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shan Wale Allah ne sadqaat ki taqseem ka masla Nabi ya kisi doosrey ki pasand par nahin chhoda balke iskey baarey mein khud hi faisla farmaya hai. aur unhen aath qism ke afrad mein taqseem farma diya hai. agar tum un mein se ho to main tumhen tumhara haq diye deta hun.''
1631,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''miskeen wo nahin jisey eik khajoor , do khajoor aur eik luqma ya do luqmey palta den balke miskeen wo hai jo logon se maangta na ho aur na logon ko uskey baarey mein andaza ho ke usey den.''"
1632,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : (aur hadees bayan ki) jaisey ke ooper guzri hai (aur) farmaya : ''lekin miskeen to wo hai jo (sawal ki aar (sharm) sey) bachta aur paak ho. ... Musaddad ne apni riwayat mein ziyada kiya ke uskey paas is qadr na ho jo ke uski kifaayat karey. ... aur wo logon se maangta bhi na ho aur na logon ko uski zarurat ka ilm ho ke wo usko sadqa den isi qism ka aadmi ''mehroom'' kahlaataa hai.'' Musaddad ne apni riwayat mein : (المتعفف الذي لا يسأل) ka zikr nahin kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Muhammad bin Saur aur Abdur-Razzaaq ne Maamer se riwayat kiya hai aur unhoney ''mehroom'' ka bayan Zohri ka kalam bataya hai aur yehi ziyada sahih hai.
1633,"Ubaidullah bin Adi bin khiyaar se manqul (naqal kiya) hai, kaha ke mujhey do aadmiyon ne bataya ke wo dono Hijjatul Wadaa ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey jabkey aap sadqa taqseem farma rahey they. un dono ne bhi aap se iska sawal kiya to aapney hamein ooper se nichey (sar se paon) tak dekha. aapney dekha ke ham dono taqatwar hain, to farmaya : ''agar tum chaho to main tumhen diye deta hun magar (haqeeqat ye hai ke) is mein ghani aur taqatwar ke kamaa-khaa sakney waley ka koi hissey nahin.''"
1634,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''sadqa kisi ghani ke liye halal nahin hai aur na kisi taqatwar sahih Salim ke liye. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko Sufiyan ne Saad bin Ibrahim se usi tarah riwayat kiya hai jaisey ke Ibrahim (ibne Saad) ne. aur Shoba ne Saad se ye lafz riwayat kiye hain : ( لذي Murra قوي ( yani (qawi) ki jagah (taqatwar) kaha, jabke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baaz deegar ahadis mein (لذي Murra قوي) aur baaz mein (لذي Murra سوي) aaya hai. Ata bin Zuhair kehtey hain ke main Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se mila to unke lafz they : (إِنَّ الصَّدَقَةَ لَا تَحِلُّ لِقَوِيٍّ وَلَا لِذِي مِرَّةٍ سَوِيٍّ)"
1635,"Janab Ata bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) (Taabai) se manqul (naqal kiya) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''paanch soorton ke alawa kisi ghani ke liye sadqa halal nahin hai. (1) jo Allah ki raah mein ghaazi aur Mujahid ho. (2) ya sadqaat ka tahseeldaar (wasul kerney wala) ho. (3) ya chattii bharney wala ho. (4) ya jo apney maal se sadqe ki chiz kharid ley. (5) ya wo aadmi ke koi miskeen uska hamsaaya ho, us miskeen ko sadqa diya gaya to usney us mein se ghani ko hadiya dey diya ho.''"
1636,Janab Ata bin Yasar Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko ibne-Uena ne Zaid se usi tarah riwayat kiya jaisey ke Malik ne kaha. aur Sauri ne Zaid se riwayat kartey huey kaha : (حدثني الثبت an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) yani eik baa-eitimaad aadmi ne merey samney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees bayan ki.
1637,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sadqa kisi ghani ke liye halal nahin hai. siwaey iske ke wo Allah ki raah mein (Mujahid) ho ya musafir ho ya kisi faqeer hamsaaey ko sadqa diya gaya to wo faqir tumhen hadiya dey dey, ya aap ki dawat kar dey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Faraas aur ibne-Abi Leila ne Atiya sey, unhoney Abu-Saeed se aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se isi ke jaise riwayat kiya hai."
1638,Hazrat Sehal bin Abi Hasma Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko sadqe ke oonton se diyat ada ki thi. yani us Ansari ki diyat jo khaibar mein qatl kar diya gaya tha.
1639,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''sawal karna apney aap ko nochna hai, is se insan apna chehra chheelta aur nochta hai. chunanche jo chahey apney chehrey ki aabroo baqi rakhey aur jo chahey zaya kar dey, taaham (fir bhi) agar koi hukmran se sawal karey ya bahut hi laachaar ho jaey, to koi muzaaeqa (haraj) nahin.''"
1640,"Hazrat Qabisa bin Makhaariq Hilaali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (eik dafa) main kisi ka zaamin (zamaanat dene wala) bin gaya. phir main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aapney farmaya : ''Qabisa ! thehrey raho yahan tak ke hamarey paas koi sadqa aa jaey to ham us mein se tumhen deney ka hukm den.'' phir farmaya : ''aey Qabisa ! sawal karna halal nahin, siwaye teen mein se eik ke : kisi ne koi zamanat li ho to uskey liye sawal karna jayez hai yahan tak ke apni zarurat puri kar ley , phir ruk jaey. doosra wo aadmi ke us par koi aisi aafat ya musibat aa padi jisney uska maal tabah kar diya to aisey shakhs ke liye sawal karna halal hai yahan tak ke guzaarey ke layaq apni zarooriyaat hasil kar ley. aur teesra wo aadmi jisey intehai ehtiyaaj (zaroorat) ne aa liya ho yahan tak ke uski qaum ke teen aql mand afrad keh den ke falan be-had laachaar ho gaya hai to usey bhi sawal karna halal hai yahan tak ke guzraan hasil kar ley aur phir ruk jaey. in soorton ke alawa sawal karna aey Qabisa ! haram hai, maangney wala haram khata hai.''"
1641,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik Ansari Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya wo kuchh mang raha tha. aapney farmaya : ''kya tumharey ghar mein kuchh nahin hai?'' kehney laga : kyon nahin, eik kamli si hai, uska eik hissey odh letey hain aur kuchh bichha letey hain aur eik piyala hai jis se pani peetey hain. aapney farmaya : ''ye dono merey paas ley aao.'' chunanche wo ley aaya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen apney haath mein liya aur farmaya : ''kaun ye chizen khareedtaa hai?'' eik shakhs ne kaha : main unhen eik dirham mein leta hun. aapney farmaya : ''eik dirham se ziyada kaun deta hai?'' aapney do ya teen baar farmaya. eik (aur) shakhs ne kaha : main inke do dirham deta hun. chunanche aapney dono chizen usey dey dien aur do dirham ley liye aur wo dono us Ansari ko dey diye aur us se farmaya : ''eik dirham ka tuaam (khana) kharido aur apney ghar walon ko dey aao aur doosrey se kulhaada kharid kar merey paas ley aao.'' chunanche wo ley aaya to aapney us mein apney dast Mubarak se dasta thonk diya aur farmaya : ''jao ! lakdiyan kaato aur becho aur pandarah din tak main tumhen na dekhun.'' chunanche wo shakhs chala gaya, lakdiyan kaat'taa aur farokht karta raha. phir aaya aur usey das dirham miley they. kuchh ka usney kapda kharida aur kuchh se khaney peeney ki chizen, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye us se behtar hai ke maangney se terey chehrey par qiyamat ke din dagh hon. bila-shuba maangna munasib nahin hai siwaye teen aadmiyon ke : had se zyada faqeer, mohtaj khaak nasheen k , ya be-chaini mein mubtala qarz daar ke, ya diyat mein padey khoon waley ke (jis par khoon ki diyat lazim ho.'')"
1642,"Janab Abu-Muslim Kholani se marwi (bayan) hai ke mujhey eik Habib (piyaarey) aur ameen shakhs ne hadees bayan ki. wo merey mehboob aur merey nazdik ameen hain (yani) Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) , wo bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein saat ya aath ya nau afrad they, to aapney farmaya : ''kya tum Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baiat nahin kar letey? ''halanke abhi ham taza taza baiat kar chukey they. ham ne kaha : ham baiat kar chukey hain, magar aapney apni baat teen baar dohraee. to ham ne apney haath badha diye aur aap se baiat ki. eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham (is se pehley) aap se baiat kar chukey hain to ab kis baat par baiat keren? aapney farmaya : ''(is baat par ke) Allah hi ki ibadat karogey, uskey sath kisi chiz ko shareek nahin karogey, paanchon namaazen ada karogey aur (ehkame shariyat aur hukkaam ki baat) suno gey aur mano gey.'' aur eik baat aahista se farmaee : ''logon se kuchh nahin maango gey.'' bayan kiya ke phir un logon ka haal ye tha ke agar kisi ki koi chhadi bhi gir jati to wo kisi aur ko ye na kehta tha ke ye utha kar mujhey dey do. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Hisham ki hadees ko Saeed ke siwa kisi aur ne riwayat nahin kiya."
1643,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai aur ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke maula (ghulam aur khaadim) they. bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kaun hai jo mujhey ye zamanat dey ke wo logon se kuch nahin maangey ga to main uskey liye jannat ki zamanat dun?'' to Hazrat Soban ne kaha : main, chunanche wo kisi se kuchh na manga kartey they."
1644,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke ansaar ke kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kiya to aapney unko inayat farmaya. unhoney phir sawal kiya to aapney aur diya yahan tak ke jo kuch aap ke paas tha, jab sab khatam ho gaya to aapney farmaya : ''merey paas jo maal bhi hoga wo main tum se hergiz bacha kar nahin rakhun ga. aur jo sawal se bachey ga Allah usey bachaey ga, jo beniyaazi ikhtiyar kerega Allah usko ghani bana dega. aur jo koi sabr kerega, Allah usey sabir bana dega. aur sabr se badh kar koi aisi nemat wasee (azeem) nahin hai jo Allah ne kisi ko di ho.''"
1645,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey intehai shadeed hajat aa padey aur usney usey logon par pesh kar diya to uski wo hajat door na hogi. aur jisney usey Allah par pesh kiya to an-qareeb Allah taala usey be-parwa kar dega. ya to jald hi maut aa jaeygi (aur duniya ke bakhedon se jaan chhoot jaeygi) ya jald hi ghani ho jaeyga (aur kisi ki ehtiyaaj (zaroorat) na rahegi).''"
1646,"ibne Al Faarsi se riwayat hai ke Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main sawal kar liya karun? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, agar zarur hi maangna ho to saleh aur nek bandon se sawal kar liya karo.''"
1647,"Hazrat ibne Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey sadqe ka tahseeldaar bana kar bheja. jab main us kaam se farigh ho kar aaya aur jama honey waley sadqe unko pesh kiye to unhoney merey baarey mein hukm diya ke usey uska haq-ul-khidmat diya jaey. maine kaha : (nahin) maine ye kaam Allah ke liye kiya hai aur mera ajr Allah par hai. unhoney farmaya : jo tumhen diya ja raha hai wo ley lo. maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein (isi qism ka ( kaam kiya tha, to aapney mujhey uska haq-ul-khidmat diya tha. maine bhi tumhari tarah ka jawab diya tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha : ''jab tumhen koi chiz bin maangey di jaey to (ley lo aur) khao aur sadqa karo.''"
1648,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne member par chadh kar farmaya jabke aap sadqa aur us se bachney (ki fazilat) aur sawal kerney (ki mazammat) bayan kar rahey they, farmaya : ''ooper wala haath, nichey waley haath se behtar hai. ooper wala haath kharch kerney wala hota hai aur nichey wala haath sawali. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat mein Ayub par, jo Naafe se riwayat kartey hain, ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai. Abdul-Waris ne kaha : ooper waley haath se murad ''(المتعففة)'' hai yani jo sawal na karey. jabke ba-waasta Hammad bin Zaid , Ayub se riwayat kerney waley aksar hazraat ooper waley haath se murad ''(المنفقة)'' yani kharch kerney wala bayan kartey hain. Hammad se sirf eik raawi (Musaddad bin Musrahid) ne (المتعففة) zikr kiya hai."
1649,"Hazrat Malik bin Nazlaa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haath teen tarah ke hain : eik haath Allah ka hai jo sab se ooper hai. doosra deney waley ka hai jo uskey baad hai aur saail ka haath sab se nichey hai, lihaza jo zayed ho, wo dey do. aur apney nafs ke samney aajiz (majboor) mat bano (us ka kaha mat mano).''"
1650,"Ibne-Abi Raafe Hazrat Abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bani makhzoom ke eik shakhs ko sadqaat ke liye muqarrar kiya, usney Abu-Raafe se kaha : merey sath chalo, tumhen bhi us se hissey milega. usney kaha : pehley mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se ho aaun aur aap se poochh lun, chunanche wo aap ki khidmat mein aaya aur aap se poochha, to aapney farmaya : ''qaum ka maula (azad shuda ghulam) unhi mein se hota hai aur hamarey liye sadqa halal nahin hai.''"
1651,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi giri padi khajoor ke paas se guzartey to usko utha leney se sirf isliye gurez kartey ke kahin sadqey ki na ho.
1652,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (kisi raastey mein) eik khajoor pai, to farmaya : ''agar mujhey ye andesha na hota ke ye sadqey ki hogi to main isey kha leta. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke isey Hisham ne Qatada se isi tarah riwayat kiya hai."
1653,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke merey walid ne mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja, un oonton ke silsiley mein jo aapney unhen sadqe se diye they."
1654,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se mazkura baala ki manind marwi (bayan) hai (Abu-Ubaida ne ( ye izafa kiya. ... ke merey walid ne mujhey bheja ke aap un oonton ko badal den.
1655,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein gosht pesh kiya gaya to aapney puchha : ''ye kya hai?'' kehney lagey : Barira ko sadqa diya gaya tha (ye usi mein se hai.) aapney farmaya : ''wo uskey liye sadqa aur hamarey liye hadiya hai.''
1656,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur kehney lagi ke maine apni walida ko eik londi bataur sadqa di thi jabke walida ab faut ho gaee hai aur wo londi apney tarkey mein chhod gaee hai. aapney farmaya : ''tera ajr aur sawab Sabit ho gaya aur wo londi virasat mein tujhey laut aai.''
1657,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein (الماعون) se murad ye letey they ke kisi ko istimal ki gharz se aariyatan (udhaar) dol dey diya ya handiya dey di.
1658,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi sahibe-khazana uska haq ada na karta raha ho, tu Allah taala qiyamat ke roz us maal ko is tarah kar dega ke jahannam ki aag se usey tapaya jaeyga , phir us se is (ke malik) ki peshani, pehlu aur kamar ko daaghaa jaeyga yahan tak ke Allah taala apney bandon mein faisla farmaeyga, us roz ke jiski tawaalat (lambaai) tumharey shumar se pachas hazar saal hai, uskey baad wo apni raah dekhega , jannat ki taraf ya jahannam ki taraf. aur jo koi bakriyon wala unka haq ada na karta raha tha, to qiyamat ke roz un bakriyon ko laya jaeyga , us se ziyada farba haalat mein jitni ke wo pehley thin , aur isey eik saaf chatiyal maidan mein ondha litaa diya jaeyga, chunanche wo bakriyan usey apney seengon se maarna aur apney khuron se raundna shuru kerengi aur un mein koi bhi mudey huey seengon wali ya be seengon ke na hogi. jiyon-hi (unka eik chakkar pura hoga aur) aakhiri bakri guzrey gi pehley wali ko us par lautaya jaeyga yahan tak ke Allah taala apney bandon mein faisla farmaeyga, us din ke jiski tawaalat tumharey hisab se pachas hazar saal hai, uskey baad apni raah dekhega , jannat ki taraf ya jahannam ki taraf . aur jo koi oonton wala unka haq ada na karta raha tha, to qiyamat ke roz unhen laya jaeyga , us se ziyada farba haalat mein , jitney ke wo us se pehley they. aur Malik ko eik saaf chatiyal maidan mein ondha litaa diya jaeyga aur phir wo usey apney pairon se raundna shuru kar dengey jiyon-hi (unka eik chakkar pura ho kar) aakhiri oont guzrey ga, pehley waley ko lautaya jaeyga yahan tak ke Allah taala apney bandon mein faisla farmaeyga, us din ke jiski tawaalat tumharey shumar mein pachas hazar saal hai, phir uskey baad wo apni raah dekhega, jannat ki taraf ya jahannam ki taraf.''"
1659,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ki manind bayan kiya. aur oonton ke bayan mein jo zikr hua ke ''jo unke haq ada na karta raha tha.'' . ... ke baad kaha . ... ''aur unke haq mein se ye hai ke jis din unhen pani pilaney ke liye laye unka doodh dohey.''
1660,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi (mazkura baala) qissey ki manind suna. shagrid ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke oonton ka kya haq hai? unhoney kaha : to behtareen oont dedey (Allah ki raah mein), ziyada doodh deney wali oontni Atiya kar dey, koi sawari aariyatan dey dey, aur jufti ke liye nar dey dey aur logon ko doodh pila dey."
1661,Hazrat Ubaid bin Umair (Rahimahullah) ( Taabai ( bayan kartey hain ke eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! oonton ka kya haq hai? to mazkura baala ki manind zikr kiya aur mazeed kaha : ''uska dol aariyatan (udhaar) dey dena.''
1662,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khajuron ka phal todney waley sab logon ko hukm diya tha ke jo koi das wasq khajoor kaatey wo eik khosha miskeenon  ke liye masjid mein latka diya karey.
1663,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they ke eik aadmi apni oontni par aaya aur usey daain baeyn ghumaaney laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jiskey paas koi zayed sawari ho wo us shakhs ko dey dey jiskey paas sawari na ho. aur jiskey paas khaney peeney ki koi zayed chiz ho wo us shakhs ko dey dey jiskey paas tosha na ho.'' (aap ke is irshad sey) ham ne ye samjha ke hamarey zayed amwaal mein hamara koi haq nahin hai.
1664,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul (naqal hui) hai ke jab ye aayat kareema (وَالَّذِينَ يَكْنِزُونَ الذَّهَبَ وَالْفِضَّة) nazil hui to is se musalmanon ko bahut girani hui. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main tumhari mushkil door karta hun, chunanche wo sab aaye aur unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! aap ke as-haab ko ye aayat bahut bhari mehsoos ho rahi hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ne Zakat farz hi isliye ki hai ke us se tumhara baqiiya maal paak ho jaey. aur virasat isliye farz farmaee hai ke tumharey baad walon ko miley.'' is par Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ( الله اكبر ( phir aapney is se farmaya : ''kya main tujhey khabar na dun ke wo kya behtareen chiz hai jo insan khazana banata hai?'' farmaya : ''wo nek saalah biwi hai, jab uski taraf dekhay to usey khush kar dey, usey koi baat kahe to maan ley aur jab wo ghayeb ho to us (ke ghar , maal aur apni iffat) ki hifazat karey.''"
1665,"Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''saail ka haq hai, chahey (chaahe) wo ghodey hi par Sawar ho kar aaye.''"
1666,"Hazrat Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne apney walid Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se. ... mazkura baala hadees ke jaisi riwayat ki."
1667,"Hazrat Umme-Bajeed (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai aur wo un aurton mein se thin jinhon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baiat ki thi. unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki aap par rahmatein nazil hon, miskeen merey darwazey par aa khada hota hai aur merey paas usey deney ko kuchh nahin hota jo main usey dun? aapney farmaya : ''agar tumhen usey deney ko kuchh na miley , aur tumharey paas bakri ka jala hua khur hi ho to wohi uskey haath mein dey do.''"
1668,"Hazrat Asma Binte-Abi Bakar (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, bayan karti hain ke Quraish ke sath muahida hudaibiya ke dinon mein meri walida merey paas (Madiney mein) aai jabke wo (Islam ko) napasand karti thi aur mushrik thi. maine puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri walida merey yahan aai hai aur (Islam ko) napasand karti hai aur mushrik hai. kya main uskey sath Husne sulook karun? aapney farmaya : '' haan apni maa ke sath Husne sulook aur sila rahmi ka mamla karo.''"
1669,"Baheesa (Raziallahu anha) apney walid se naqal karti hain ke merey walid ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se milney ki ijazat chahi. aur wo aap ki qamis aur aap ke darmiyan dakhil ho gaey aur aap ka jism choomney aur us se lipatney lagey. phir kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo kya cheez hai jis ka rok lena halal nahin? aapney farmaya : ''pani.'' phir puchha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! wo kya cheez hai jis ka rok lena halal nahin? farmaya : ''namak.'' phir puchha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! wo kya cheez hai jis ka rok lena halal nahin? aapney farmaya : ''jo bhalai bhi tum karo, wo tumharey liye khair hai.''"
1670,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''kya tum mein koi hai jisney aaj kisi miskeen ko khana khilaya ho?'' to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : main masjid mein dakhil ho raha tha to maine eik saail ko sawal kartey huey dekha, maine (apney sahibzadey) Abdur-Rehman ke haath mein roti ka eik tukda paya, to wo maine us se lekar us saail ko dey diya."
1671,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke chehrey ka wasta de-kar sirf jannat hi ka sawal kiya ja sakta hai.''"
1672,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ke wastey se panah maangey usko aman do . aur jo shakhs Allah ke naam se sawal karey usko do . aur jo tumhari dawat karey uski dawat qubul karo. aur jo tumharey sath ehsan karey uska badla do . agar badla deney ke liye koi chiz na pao to uskey haq mein dua karo yahan tak ke tum samajh lo ke us (ke ehsan (ka badla dey diya hai.''"
1673,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein they ke achcha eik aadmi aaya, uskey paas andey ke barabar sona tha, kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool! mujhey ye eik kaan se mila hai aap usey ley lijiye, ye sadqa hai, merey paas uskey ilawa aur kuch nahin hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se munh pher liya, to wo aap ki daain janib se aaya aur pehley ki tarah kaha. aapney us se munh pher liya . to wo aap ki baain janib se aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne munh pher liya. phir wo aap ke peechey se aaya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se wo sona lekar phenk diya. agar wo usey lagta to us se usko chot lagti balke wo usey zakhmi kar deta. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi apna sab maal lekar aa jata hai aur kehta hai ke ye sadqa hai. phir logon se maangney beth jata hai. behtareen sadqa wohi hai jo apni zarurat puri kerney ke baad diya jaey.''"
1674,ibne-Is-haq ne apni mazkura sanad se aur usi ke ham-maani bayan kya. us mein mazeed ye hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ham se apna maal ley jao hamen uski koi zarurat nahin.'' ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey qubul nahin farmaya.)
1675,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi masjid mein dakhil hua to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon ko hukm diya ke kapdey do ( sadqa ke taur par (aur us ( aaney waley (ke baarey mein farmaya ke usey do kapdey de-do . aapney phir ( dobara ( sadqey ki targheeb di to us shakhs ne bhi apna eik kapda phenk diya. aapney usey daant kar farmaya : '' apna kapda utha lo .''
1676,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba behtareen sadqa wo hai jo ghina (logon se be-niazi) ko baqi rehney dey ya ye ke us keyfiyat mein sadqa kya jaey ke khud mohtaj aur zarurat mand na ho (balke ghani ho) aur un se shuru karo jin ki kafalat ke tum zimmedar ho.''
1677,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, unhoney puchha ke aey Allah ke Rasool! kon-sa sadqa afzal hai? aapney farmaya : ''kam maal waley ka mehnat mashaqqat karkey dena. aur shuru un se karo jin ki kafalat ke tum zimmedar ho.''"
1678,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen sadqa kerney ka hukm diya. us moqe par merey paas maal bhi tha. chunanche maine ( dil mein) kaha : agar main abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se sabqat lena chahun to aaj ley sakta hun. chunanche main apna aadha maal (aap ki khidmat mein) ley aaya . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''tum ne apney ghar walon ke liye kya baqi chhoda hai?'' maine kaha : isi qadr ( chhod aaya hun (aur phir Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apna kul maal (aap ke paas ( ley aaye . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha : ''tum ne apney ghar walon ke liye kya baqi chhoda hai?'' kaha : maine unke liye Allah aur uskey Rasool ko chhoda hai. tab mujhey kehna pada : main kisi cheez mein kabhi bhi un se nahin badh sakta.
1679,Hazrat Saad (bin Ubada) (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur puchha ke aap ke nazdik kon sa sadqa ziyada pasandida hai? aapney farmaya : '' pani .''
1680,"Muhammad bin abdur-Raheem apni sanad se Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kartey hain."
1681,"Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ( meri walida ( Umme- Saad faut ho gaee hain to kon sa sadqa afzal hai? (jo main unki taraf se karun) aapney farmaya : '' pani .'' chunanche unhoney eik kunwan khudwaya aur kaha ke ye ( meri walida ( Umme- Saad ki taraf se hai."
1682,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jo musalman kisi musalman ko kapda pahnaaey jabkey wo nanga ho to Allah taala usey jannat ki sabz (hari) paushaak pahnaaeyga. aur jis musalman ne kisi musalman ko khilaya jabkey wo bhuka ho to Allah usey jannat ke phalon se khilaaeyga. aur jis musalman ne kisi musalman ko pilaya jabkey wo piyasa ho to Allah usey jannat ki khalis sharab se palaeyga.''
1683,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chaalis khaslaton mein se sab se achchi khaslat '' doodh ki bakri '' hadiya karna hai, jo koi banda unke sawab ki umeed aur un par kiye gaey wadey ki tasdeeq ki bina par kisi eik par bhi amal kar ley tu Allah usey uskey sabab jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Musaddad ki riwayat mein Hassan bin Atiya ne kaha : ham ne doodh ki bakri ke hadiya ke ilawa ( deegar aamaal maslan ( salam aur chheenk ka jawab dena aur raastey se aziyat wali chiz door karna , waghera shumar kerney ki koshish ki magar pandarah khaslaton tak bhi nahin pahunch sakey .) maloom nahin wo kon kon si hain. ("
1684,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba amanat daar khazaanchi jo Malik ke hukm ke mutabiq dil ki khushi se pura pura dey, yahan tak ke jiskey mutalliq kaha gaya hai usey dey dey , wo do sadqa kerney walon mein se eik hai. ( eik asal Malik jisney deney ka hukm diya aur doosra ye jisney ada kya. ("
1685,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' biwi jab apney shohar ke ghar se kharch karey (sadqa dey) jabkey israaf kerney wali na ho to usey sadqa kerney ka aur uskey shohar ko kama laney ka sawab hai aur uskey khazaanchi ko bhi usi qadr hai, un mein se koi bhi kisi ka ajr kam nahin karta.''"
1686,"Hazrat Saad (bin abi Waqas ( (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurton se baiat li to eik ba-waqar (ya lambey qad wali) aurat khadi hui , goya ke wo qabeela Muzar se thi , kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Nabi ! ham to apney maa baap , apney beton . ... . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha mera khayal hai usney shohron ka zikr bhi kya. ... par bojh hain to hamarey liye unke maalon mein se kya halal hai? aapney farmaya : '' (tar chizen khao aur hadiya bhi do. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ( رطب ( '' tar '' se murad : roti , tarkaari aur taza khajoor hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : Sauri ne bhi Yunus se aisey hi riwayat ki hai."
1687,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aurat apney khawind ki kamai se uskey kahey baghair sadqa dey to usey uskey shohar ka aadha sawab hai.''"
1688,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu)) se puchha gaya ke) kya aurat apney shohar ke ghar se sadqa dey (ya na dey ( ? unhoney kaha : nahin, apney hissey ke kharch se dey sakti hai, (jo shohar ne usey diya ho.) aur ajr un dono ke beech hoga. aur uskey liye halal nahin ke shohar ke maal se uski ijazat ke baghair sadqa karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye fatwa goya sabiqa hadees Hammam ki tazeef hai."
1689,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab aayat kareema : ( لنْ تَنَالُوا الْبِرَّ حَتَّى تُنْفِقُوا مِمَّا تُحِبُّونَ ( nazil hui to Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! main samajhta hun ke hamara rab ham se hamarey maal maangta hai to aap gawah rahen ke maine apni (ariha) wali zameen Allah ke liye di , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey apney rishte-daaron mein taqseem kar do .'' chunanche unhoney usey Hassaan bin Sabit aur Ubai bin Kab mein taqseem kar diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke mujhey Ansari Muhammad bin Abdullah se ye baat pahunchi hai ke Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka nasab yun hai : abu-Talha : Zaid bin Sehal bin Aswad bin haram bin Amr bin Zaid Manaata bin Adi bin Amr bin Malik bin Najjaar. aur Hazrat Hassaan (Raziallahu anhu) ka nasab is tarah hai : Hannan bin Sabit bin Munzir bin Haram. abu-Talha aur Hassaan dono teesrey baap yani (pardaada) haram par jama hotey hain. aur abi (Raziallahu anhu) ka nasab ye hai : Ubai bin Kab bin Qais bin Ateek bin Zaid bin Muawiya bin Amr bin Malik bin Najjaar. Amr ( Amr Malik ( un teeno ko jama karta hai. yani Hassaan , abu-Talha aur abi ko . Ansari ne wazahat ki ke abi aur abu-Talha mein chatey baap mein ja kar rishta judta hai."
1690,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai wo bayan karti hain ke meri eik londi thi, maine usey aazad kar diya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laey, maine aap ko bataya to aapney farmaya : ''Allah tujhey jaza dey, taaham to agar usey apney mamun ko dey deti to terey liye ziyada sawab hota .''"
1691,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sadqa kerney ka hukm diya to eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey paas eik Dinar hai, aapney farmaya : '' apni jaan par sadqa kar .'' kehney laga : merey paas doosra hai. farmaya : '' apney bachey par sadqa kar .'' kehney laga : merey paas eik aur hai. farmaya : '' apni biwi par sadqa kar .'' lafz ( زوجتك (ya ( زوجك ( farmaya , kehney laga : merey paas eik aur hai. farmaya : '' apney khaadim par sadqa kar .'' kehney laga merey paas eik aur hai. farmaya : '' to uskey mutalliq behtar janta hai.'' (ke kahan aur kis par kharch karna hai. ("
1692,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' insan ke gunahgaar honey ke liye yehi (amal) kafi hai ke jinkey rizq w ikhrajaat ka ye zimmedar ho, unhen zaya kar dey .''"
1693,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey ye baat achi lagti ho ke uska rizq faraakh aur umr taweel ho to usey chahiye ke apney aziz w aqaarib se mail milaap rakhey.''"
1694,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap farmatey they : ''Allah taala farmata hai : main Rehman hun (be-inteha rehem kerney wala) aur ye rishte-daariyan jisey ke (reham) kehtey hain, uska lafz maine apney naam se nikala hai, to jo apney aziz qurbat daaron se mel-jol rakhta hai) sila rehmi karta hai) mein us se judta hun aur jo usko kaat'ta aur todtaa hai main us se kat jata hun.''"
1695,Muhammad bin mutawakkil Asqalani ki sanad se marwi (bayan) hai ke Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna . aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya.
1696,"Hazrat Jubair bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' qata' rehmi kerney wala jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga.''"
1697,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' badley mein mail milaap kerney wala sila rehmi kerney wala nahin hai, balke sila rehmi kerney wala wo hai jo todey janey waley rishtey ko jodey .''"
1698,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khutba diya aur farmaya : ''apney aap ko hirs w bukhl se bachao tum se pehley ke log usi wajeh se halak huey. (hirs ne) unko hukm diya to wo bukhl kerney lagey, qata' rehmi ka hukm diya to qurbat tod li aur bad-kari ka hukm diya to bad-kari kerney lagey .''"
1699,"Hazrat Asma binte-abi Bakar (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey paas bas wohi hota hai jo ( merey shohar ( Zuber ghar mein ley ayen . to kya main us se dey diya karun ? aapney farmaya : '' ( Asma ! ( do aur baandh baandh kar mat rakho , warna tum par bhi) tumhara rizq ( baandh diya jaeyga.''"
1700,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaee miskinon ko shumar kya. ... . ya kaee sadqaat ginwaaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : '' ( Aaisha ! ( do aur gino nahin, warna tumhen bhi gin-gin kar diya jaeyga.''"
